questions.question: fme_feature_type contains...
options: the full schema of the source feature type.
the name of the dataset's original features (for example, a file, feature class, database, or table).
the path to the source dataset.

questions.question: To produce a zip file output for file- and folder-based datasets, you just have to add ".zip" to the end of the Destination File/Folder parameter.
